{
  "stem": "14060.7",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We travelled two and a half days to Buchenwald, which is Turingia from the area of Auschwitz, Katowice, Silesia there, which Buchenwald is eight kilometers from Weimar in Turingia.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We went through Dresden, Chemnitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You know, we saw some of the stations.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Not a morsel of food-- this was literally probably the longest time that we had not a drop of water or anything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And it wasn't really encouraging by the time we arrived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But on the main, those people survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We arrived in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Buchenwald was not an extermination camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Even so, it was the first German concentration camp from 1933.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "That was a very organized place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We, we got in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They, they took us through, again, the motion of showers, disinfection.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we got our lager numbers and a document, which I'm pleased to provide you to, to show.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We were taken all our personal details-- our name, full name, year of birth, place, address, and the age, obviously, which is the date of birth, plus what languages one spoke, any unusual deformities, eyes color, nose, mouth, whatever you like-- comprehensive.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Now, all these records were provided in forms, which you had to sign.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And, and on the form-- can you imagine, after Birkenau-- It says that it is criminal to make a false declaration.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And you will be punished for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I mean, it seems a rather odd threat after you have been Birkenau and Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "However, one did take note of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And there was-- but nevertheless-- and one had to sign it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Now, I told you that my father was born in 1891.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He made his age 1895, four years older-- younger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "My brother was born in 1924.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He made himself younger to get closer to my age, 1926.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
